OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBBC announces restructure  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto India operations        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The BBC is restructuring its operations
OL,6, in India to comply with the country's  
OL,7, foreign investment rules.              
OL,9,FFour employees will leave the BBC to   
OL,10,Fform a wholly Indian-owned company,    
OL,11,FCollective Newsroom, containing the    
OL,12,FBBC's six Indian language services.    
OL,14,FThe broadcaster's English language     
OL,15,Fnewsgathering operation in India will  
OL,16,Fremain with the BBC.                   
OL,18,FIt follows an investigation this year  
OL,19,Fwhich saw the BBC's India offices      
OL,20,Fsearched by tax authorities.           
